---
import CompaSwag from '../components/CompaSwag.astro'
import Shell from '../layouts/Shell.astro'
---

<Shell title="Home">
	<div class="container mx-auto">
		<div class="text-secondary mx-auto max-w-[20rem] text-center font-medium">
			Bring your ideas to life with the GPT 4.1 series
		</div>

		<div class="py-16 flex justify-center">
			<div class="w-3/4 max-w-4xl">
				<CompaSwag />
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mx-auto text-center font-medium md:max-w-[35rem]">
			<span class="text-secondary">About:</span>
			<h1 class="inline">
				DevGPT turns plain‑language prompts into simple apps and sites, powered by GPT‑4.1, 4.1-mini and 4.1-nano.
			</h1>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
			<div class="w-full max-w-4xl rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
				<video
					autoplay
					loop
					muted
					playsinline
					class="w-full h-auto"
				>
					<source src="/demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
					Your browser does not support the video tag.
				</video>
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="mt-14">
			<h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-3xl font-bold md:text-5xl">
				DevGPT's powerful features <br /> to bring your ideas to life.
			</h2>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">No-Code Web Apps</h3>

					<p>
						Create fully functional web applications just by describing what you want. 
						No coding experience required. Simply explain your idea and DevGPT handles
						the implementation.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						From e-commerce to portfolios to productivity tools - all from simple text prompts.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Interactive UI</h3>

					<p>
						Get beautiful, responsive user interfaces that work across all devices.
						DevGPT creates modern designs that adapt to any screen size.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						Customize colors, layouts, and components with simple instructions.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Templates & Starter Projects</h3>

					<p>
						Jump-start your development with pre-built templates and starter projects.
						DevGPT offers a variety of foundations to build upon for common use cases.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						From landing pages to portfolios - get a head start with templates.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">API Connections</h3>

					<p>
						Connect your application with third-party services and APIs. DevGPT
						can integrate with payment processors, maps, social media, and more.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">Expand functionality without additional development.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Easy to Use</h3>

					<p>
						DevGPT features an intuitive interface that anyone can master in minutes.
						Just describe what you want in plain language and watch as your application
						takes shape.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						No technical jargon or complex workflows - just simple conversations to build your app.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Real-time Preview</h3>

					<p>
						See your application evolve as you describe new features or make changes.
						DevGPT provides instant visual feedback so you can refine your idea on the fly.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						Iterate quickly based on what you see, ensuring the final product matches your vision.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- <div class="col-span-1">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Multi-Language Support</h3>

					<p>
						DevGPT can generate applications using a wide variety of programming languages
						and frameworks based on your specific needs and preferences.
					</p>

					<p class="text-secondary mt-2">
						From JavaScript and Python to specialized frameworks like React, Vue, or Django - all available through simple text commands.
					</p>
				</div> -->
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="py-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Ready to transform your ideas into reality?</h3>
			<a href="https://gpt-4-1-use.vercel.app/" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-black dark:bg-white dark:hover:bg-zinc-200 dark:text-zinc-900 text-white font-medium py-3 px-12 rounded-full transition-all hover:shadow-md text-lg">Start Building with DevGPT</a>
		</div>

		<section class="mt-20 py-16 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-xl">
			<h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-5xl font-bold">
				DevGPT's Core Principles
			</h2>

			<div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="col-span-1 p-8 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-zinc-100 dark:border-neutral-700 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-neutral-700 mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
								<path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"></path>
								<line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line>
								<line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-center">Accessibility</h3>
						<p class="text-center">
							DevGPT makes software development accessible to everyone, not just programmers.
							We believe that anyone with an idea should be able to build it.
						</p>

						<p class="text-secondary mt-4 text-center text-sm">
							DevGPT empowers everyone.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="col-span-1 p-8 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-zinc-100 dark:border-neutral-700 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-neutral-700 mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<polyline points="13 2 13 9 20 9"></polyline>
								<path d="M13 2L2 2L2 22L22 22L22 9L13 2Z"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-center">Speed & Efficiency</h3>
						<p class="text-center">
							DevGPT reduces development time from weeks to minutes. Focus on your vision
							and content rather than coding challenges.
						</p>

						<p class="text-secondary mt-4 text-center text-sm">
							build your simple apps 10x faster.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="col-span-1 p-8 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg border border-zinc-100 dark:border-neutral-700 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-neutral-700 mx-auto mb-6">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
								<path d="M20.24 12.24a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5 10.5V19h8.5z"></path>
								<line x1="16" y1="8" x2="2" y2="22"></line>
								<line x1="17.5" y1="15" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-center">Flexibility</h3>
						<p class="text-center">
							Every application built with DevGPT is uniquely yours. Custom-tailored to your
							specific requirements and adaptable to your changing needs.
						</p>

						<p class="text-secondary mt-4 text-center text-sm">
							Start simple and evolve 
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Shell>
